01:00:20.717 --> 01:00:21.985
-Adeus. -Adeus.

01:00:22.019 --> 01:00:23.287
-Adeus. -Adeus.

01:00:23.320 --> 01:00:24.588
-Amo-te. Amo-te. -Adeus.

01:00:24.621 --> 01:00:26.190
-Amo-te. -Amo-te.

01:00:32.863 --> 01:00:34.031
Adeus.

01:00:37.535 --> 01:00:39.136
