01:05:01.466 --> 01:05:02.633
Adoro-te imenso.

01:05:02.667 --> 01:05:04.935
Barr.

01:05:06.537 --> 01:05:07.772
Oh.

01:05:07.805 --> 01:05:09.439
Estas pessoas.

01:05:09.474 --> 01:05:10.941
Espera...

